data.text:
-> SSC GD Constable Result has been declared for the Constable (GD), 2024 Examination which was conducted from 20.02.2024 to 07.03.2024 and 30.03.2024 in the Computer Based Mode.

-> The Successful Candidates have been provisionally shortlisted to appear in the PST / PET.

-> For 2025 Cycle, the Computer Based Examination will be conducted on January-February 2025.

-> Earlier, Revised Vacancy was released. A total of 46,617 vacancies have been announced for the SSC GD Constable Exam 2024, out of which 41,467 vacancies are for Male Constables while 5,150 vacancies are for Female Constables.

-> Total 16185 candidates appeared for the exam.
